description: Chicago - The Heart Of Chicago: The Videos 1982-1991 [2005] DVD5 Chicago is an American rock band formed in 1967 in Chicago, Illinois. The group had a steady stream of hits throughout the 1970s and 1980s. Second only to The Beach Boys in Billboard singles and albums chart success among American bands, Chicago is one of the longest-running and most successful rock groups, and one of the world's best-selling groups of all time, having sold more than 100 million records. The original album was released in 1997 on LD (Warner Music Vision WPLR-56) and VHS. This is a DVD transfer released in 2005.
